’Щ@dcf1a2d21c4e169af1000afa85f4ba886f319f2e7a59073329f086f7b7ef8932ЪTitle: title: polars slice
Path: Examples
Content:
Create new dataframe from a slice of the rows
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [3 4]] | polars into-df | polars slice 0 1
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
в”‚ # в”‚ a в”‚ b в”‚
в”њв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”јв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”јв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¤
в”‚ 0 в”‚ 1 в”‚ 2 в”‚
в•°в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ґв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ґв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•Ї


```
Create a new lazy dataframe from a slice of a lazy dataframe's rows
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [3 4]] | polars into-lazy | polars slice 0 1 | describe
polars_lazyframe

```
